name: Peony top
description:
Material : cotton fabric 

The Chinese heritage, full to the brim of rich history and peppered with beautiful arts, has always been a part of Judith and is something that she has always adored. This admiration is then taken and weaved into a collection called Chen Mei Zhen, which in Chinese means "beautiful and precious". The color blue, the designer's current color obsession and also a signature color in China ceramics, is dropped into the palette this time along with oriental prints. Mixed with her signature ethnic style,the collection has some edgy lines but still wearable for any occasion--light enough for hot summer days and glam enough for a cool evening out. Beautiful clothes designed especially for precious women who live an elegant life filled with optimistic outlook, just like a flower that blooms at night in all its glory even though it was dark and no one could see it.
